description: The GetCertificateVersions operation returns the versions of a certificate in the specified key vault. This operation requires the certificates/list permission.

maxresults.description: Maximum number of results to return in a page. If not specified the service will return up to 25 results.

value.description: A response message containing a list of certificates in the key vault along with a link to the next page of certificates.

nextlink.description: The URL to get the next set of certificates.
